                    <h2>Are my Last Message capsules able to be used as my video will?</h2>
                    <p>As of the time of this publication, please ask a legal professional in your country or state (each country, and state has different rules on what constitutes a legal will). We do not believe our service, as yet, is acceptable as a legally binding will.</p>

                    <h2>How does the Trustee function work?</h2>
                    <p>Trustees are appointed in the written request, and each trustee has to officially accept the responsibility of becoming your trustee. Using our proprietary technology, when our service has not heard from you in the allotted time, the Trustee Initiation Process is triggered. If you have appointed more than one trustee, both have to initiate the sequence to trigger your account deliveries.</p>
                    
